snippet.title: The Witcher 2 - PC - Preorder Trailer
snippet.description:
It is now official: Preorder for The Witcher 2 are live. Watch this new trailer to discover the content of Premium and Collector's editions.

The witcher 2 is schedule for May 17th 2011 on PC.
Join the community on http://www.facebook.com/thewitcher or get more information on your local http://www.namcobandaigames.eu website
